notifyChanges

void notifyChanges()
Notify any registered Dao.DaoObservers that the underlying data may have changed. This is done automatically when using create(Object), update(Object), or delete(Object) type methods. Batch methods will be notified once at the end of the batch, not for every statement in the batch. NOTE: The #updateRaw(String, String...) and other raw methods will _not_ call notify automatically. You will have to call this method yourself after you use the raw methods to change the entities.
